welcome_message_body: Welcome to Olivehurst, the charming city known for its beautiful parks, vibrant community, and rich history. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our city has to offer!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Yuba County Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers including dining options, restrooms, and a gift shop.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Yuba County Airport is available for use by private aircraft and offers a comfortable lounge area for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Beale AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Beale AFB Airport is reserved for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sacramento International Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Sacramento International Airport, primarily serving domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Auburn Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Auburn Airport caters to private and corporate flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Oroville Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary wifi is available throughout the terminal.
